    Get Playlist Ids

    get_playlist_ids.Rd

    Retrieves the upload playlist ids.

    Usage

    get_playlist_ids(
  client,
  token_url = "https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token",
  auth_url = "https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth",
  scope = "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/youtube"
)

    Arguments

    client

    an httr2 oauth2 client for the google api

    token_url

    google's oauth2 token url

    auth_url

    google's oauth2 auth url

    scope

    token scope, default is youtube

    Value

    list of playlist ids for uploads

    Examples

    
google_client <- construct_client()

playlist_ids <- get_playlist_ids(google_client)
#> Error in oauth_flow_check("authorization code", client, interactive = TRUE): OAuth 2.0 authorization code flow requires an interactive session
